thread.title: Danny Yi
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Danny Yi

author: Danny Yi
title: Danny Yi
text: Enquired for a delivery from vic to sa on a thursday. Package got picked up on friday and got it at the front door on monday. It was such an easy transaction and super super easy to set up delivery. Was very suprised my package came in on monday. Would definitely recommend this service to anyone!
